1
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:16,580
I know what your obsession is.

2
00:01:16,580 --> 00:01:18,289
My death is nothing to be pitied.

3
00:01:18,289 --> 00:01:20,289
I only ask two things of you, my lady.

4
00:01:20,330 --> 00:01:23,750
First, take the evidence I hid in Kunlong Valley back to the capital

5
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:26,410
to clear the names of me and my three hundred brothers.

6
00:01:26,410 --> 00:01:28,270
Second, protect my son Jingchen.

7
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:29,750
Don't let him spend his whole life

8
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:32,150
living under the stigma of a traitor's son.

9
00:01:44,700 --> 00:01:45,500
Father.

10
00:01:47,830 --> 00:01:49,950
Jingchen, guard the border well

11
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:51,370
and protect the people.

12
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:53,039
I believe in you.

13
00:02:00,540 --> 00:02:03,700
General, thirty thousand Xiongnu cavalry are charging at us.

14
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:05,410
They have broken through the outpost

15
00:02:05,410 --> 00:02:07,810
and are less than fifty miles from the camp.

16
00:02:09,539 --> 00:02:10,660
Pass on my order.

17
00:02:11,290 --> 00:02:12,620
Assemble the whole army

18
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,330
and prepare for battle.

19
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:18,620
I'll lead the medical team

20
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,079
and stay at the camp to treat the wounded.

21
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:22,210
Go to the frontline with peace of mind.

22
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,329
I'll go with you.

23
00:02:30,410 --> 00:02:32,700
The soul lamp can comfort the dead souls at the border

24
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:34,230
and protect your soldiers.

25
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:38,810
The spy who killed your father is colluding with the Xiongnu.

26
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,329
We must find him.

27
00:02:41,250 --> 00:02:44,700
I must fight this battle.

28
00:02:51,370 --> 00:02:52,160
Okay.

29
00:02:53,579 --> 00:02:54,750
I'll protect you.

30
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:05,040
Soldiers.

31
00:03:05,790 --> 00:03:07,330
The Xiongnu invade our borders,

32
00:03:07,330 --> 00:03:08,160
slaughter our cities,

33
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,620
and harm our compatriots.

34
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,370
Today, this Juma Slope

35
00:03:11,950 --> 00:03:13,700
will be their burial ground.

36
00:03:13,950 --> 00:03:15,410
Defend the land of Dayong

37
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:17,160
and protect the people behind us!

38
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,370
Charge with me!

39
00:03:18,579 --> 00:03:21,329
Kill!

40
00:03:21,620 --> 00:03:22,500
Kill!

41
00:03:24,290 --> 00:03:28,079
Defend our land and protect our country.

42
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,410
Burn their supplies.

43
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:22,960
Let's see how they fight without them.

44
00:04:36,659 --> 00:04:37,620
Brothers.

45
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:40,620
Supplies are the lifeblood of the army.

46
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:44,080
We'd rather die than let the Xiongnu take a single step inside.

47
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,659
The territory of Dayong

48
00:04:58,409 --> 00:05:00,620
cannot be trampled by scums like you!

49
00:05:02,450 --> 00:05:03,250
What's going on?

50
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:04,200
Why are the horses startled?

51
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,910
Charge! Charge forward!

52
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:12,160
Leave no one alive! Kill!

53
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:13,410
Give me your life!

54
00:05:54,409 --> 00:05:55,200
Father.

55
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:58,110
I didn't disgrace the Xie family.

56
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:13,500
The war has ended,

57
00:06:14,250 --> 00:06:15,580
the country is at peace,

58
00:06:16,370 --> 00:06:18,030
and earthly ties are severed.

59
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,200
Rest in peace.

60
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:38,950
Father.

61
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,409
I guarded the border

62
00:06:42,909 --> 00:06:44,510
and the territory of Dayong.

63
00:06:45,909 --> 00:06:50,440
The grievances of you and the three hundred brothers will eventually be cleared.

64
00:06:51,909 --> 00:06:52,830
Good boy.

65
00:06:56,450 --> 00:06:58,380
You didn't disgrace the Xie family

66
00:06:58,659 --> 00:07:00,700
or the soldiers of Dayong.

67
00:07:01,370 --> 00:07:03,830
I am proud of you.

68
00:07:09,910 --> 00:07:10,700
Xie Lin.

69
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:16,370
It's been ten years, time to wake up.

70
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:17,830
Kill them

71
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,540
and destroy the soul lamp.

72
00:07:31,410 --> 00:07:34,080
Oh no, his soul has been infected by evil energy.

73
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:56,409
Father, what's wrong?

74
00:07:56,409 --> 00:07:58,080
Wake up.

75
00:07:58,080 --> 00:08:00,250
It's me, Jingchen.

76
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:18,620
Jingchen.

77
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,830
This move, horizontal river cleave,

78
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:22,500
requires strength from your waist and abdomen,

79
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:24,230
not brute force from your arms.

80
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:26,620
Remember.

81
00:08:27,330 --> 00:08:28,750
A sword is for protecting the country

82
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,080
and your loved ones.

83
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,720
It is not for hurting people.

84
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:37,000
Father, no!

85
00:09:52,250 --> 00:09:55,830
Good boy! You are indeed Xie Lin's son.

86
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:07,200
You've grown up. You can draw my bow now.

87
00:10:07,370 --> 00:10:09,160
In the future, this border

88
00:10:09,370 --> 00:10:10,830
and the land of Dayong

89
00:10:10,950 --> 00:10:13,250
will depend on you boys to protect.

90
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:18,750
Jingchen, watch out!

91
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:22,110
Demonic forces have infiltrated the mortal realm.

92
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,290
In the royal court,

93
00:10:24,950 --> 00:10:26,830
there are traps everywhere.

94
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:30,580
Their target is the Soul Lamp

95
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:32,660
and the land of Dayong.

96
00:10:35,330 --> 00:10:36,910
I'm sorry.

97
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:40,290
I failed to protect you.
